      <div class="msgContentFrame">The karma system isn't working as it should on this (the FFXIV) board.  (Although some will argue it is.) <br /> <br />The general forum either needs to be properly moderated and trouble posters need to be dealt with.   <br /> <br />It's getting out of hand that every single thread is devolved by some idiot coming in posting absolutely nothing to the conversation and them not getting sub-defaulted because the rest of the trolls/socks are right there to vote them up.  The real kicker is they get that privliage after just a handful of trolling posts.  &quot;lolz, you all have ocd cause this game sucks, only someone with ocd could possible find it fun, lolz!!!!!111one&quot; as a first post lands someone scholar status..  <br /> <br />I know this is going to come across as whiny because I can't but I'm positive there are many more in the same boat I am.  We have provided countless posts in aid of the community but still have yet to rise above whatever the default level is and is a load of bullsh*t that the people who actually assist and provide actual information with data to back it are held at the whim of the trolls infesting the FFXIV boards.   <br /> <br />That's it... I know no one likes to hear someone bitch about the karma system but it is clearly not working on that board.  Maybe ratings for posts on that forum need weighted differently... I don't know your the ones being paid... </div>
