        <div class="msgUM"><a class="msgWhoName Administrator" href="/users/Kaolian">Pumpkin LÃ¶rd Kaolian</a><div class="msgWhoTitle Administrator">Leet Hax&#246;r</div><div class="msgUMex"><a href="/journal.html?user=4491" class="icon-userjournal">View Journal</a></div></div><div class="msgAvatar"><img alt="Avatar" height="120" width="120" src="http://common.allakhazam.com/images/2/2/22a0fe21fcf0abc064481c37e1f58fee.jpg"/></div><div class="msgStar"><span class="bright">In Soviet Russia, 20k gets Admin!</span></div><div class="msgWhoNum">25,799 posts</div>
